                <h1 class="cover-text-title">14 Patterns of Biophilic Design</h1>
                <p class="cover-text-subtitle">Improving Health & Well-Being in the Built Environment</p>
                <img class="cover-logo" src="img/logo-full-white.png" alt="Terrapin Bright Green">
