                                </p>-->

                                <p id="footnote-001" class="anchor">
                                    Alcock, I., M.P. White, B.W. Wheeler, L.E. Fleming, & M.H. Depledge. (2014). <cite>Longitudinal Effects on Mental Health of Moving to Greener and Less Green Urban Areas</cite>. Environmental Science & Technology, 48 (2), 1247-1255.
                                    <a href="#footnote-mark-021" class="footnote-back-link">21<i class="fa fa-level-up"></i></a>
                                </p>

